structure.unit: RURAL ELECTRIC AND RURAL TELEPHONE COOPERATIVE CORPORATIONS

law.history: Repealed and reenacted 2010 Ky. Acts ch. 51, sec. 133, effective July 15, 2010; and repealed ch. 151, sec. 151, effective January 1, 2011. -- Amended 2007 Ky. Acts ch. 137, sec. 133, effective June 26, 2007. -- Amended 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 38, sec. 5, effective June 21, 1974. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. secs. 883j-6, 883j-9.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Use of "Rural Electric Cooperative" in name limited.
